WEBVTT

00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.465
(Laughter)

00:01:01.489 --> 00:01:05.799
sums up very nicely
three common beliefs we have

00:01:05.823 --> 00:01:07.682
about children and lying.

00:01:08.140 --> 00:01:12.771
One, children only come to tell lies

00:01:12.795 --> 00:01:15.063
after entering elementary school.

00:01:15.552 --> 00:01:17.863
Two, children are poor liars.

00:01:17.887 --> 00:01:20.744
We adults can easily detect their lies.

00:01:20.768 --> 00:01:24.806
And three, if children lie
at a very young age,

00:01:24.830 --> 00:01:27.679
there must be some
character flaws with them,

00:01:27.703 --> 00:01:31.752
and they are going to become
pathological liars for life.